   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1869_07_13_Reddelien_n.a._von_W_Patow_Yokohama_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>private Yokohama, 13th July 1869<lb/> ⟨Wm. Patow<lb/> r[eceived]/ 13th July⟩<lb/>Dear
                Mr. Reddelin.<lb/>I am writing these private lines to you because I<lb/>would like
                to have the lot[?] by Neels. This is because<lb/>I have been intending to set up a
                store + auction business there<lb/>and have for a long time been searching for a
                suitable place <lb/>in that area. I cannot buy a large lot as I <lb/>have not got
                the capital to do that. I have been<lb/>planning to use the downstairs space for
                myself <lb/>and to rent out part of the upper store. I am not able<lb/>to open such
                a store + auction business here in this<lb/>building as you will surely
                understand,<lb/>the place there would suit me very well indeed<lb/>and if you could
                be of assistance to me in <lb/>purchasing this, I would be most gratefully
                <lb/>indebted to you. <lb/>
         </p>
         <table>
            <row>
               <cell>I calculate 140 Itzebu c $ 10. ⁒ 5 %</cell>
               <cell>1,330.-</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell>as sold to Wyttenbach</cell>
               <cell/>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell>The house cost him more but</cell>
               <cell>1,500.-</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell>can be built for 1500.-</cell>
               <cell/>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell/>
               <cell>Total $ 2,830.-</cell>
            </row>
         </table>
         <p>Accordingly, my offer of 3,500.- ⁒ 5% seems to me to <lb/>be a very reasonable one.
                Everyone knows that he paid <lb/>too much for the land + house. As promised, before
                you<lb/>decide in one way or another, I am expecting to hear from <lb/>you as I
                really would very much like to purchase the place <lb/>in order to carry out my
                above intentions. </p>
         <pb facs="1869_07_13_Reddelien_n.a._von_W_Patow_Yokohama_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>Best wishes<lb/>W<lb/>W Patow</p>
      </body>
   </text>
